                Storyline Entertainment(2008). Length : 97min                 


 Corprate billionaire Edward Cole and working class mechanic Carter Chambers  
 have nothing in common except for their terminal illnesses. While sharing a  
 hospital room together, they decide to leave it and do all the things they   
 have ever wanted to do before they die according to their bucket list. In    
 the process, both of them heal each other, become unlikely friends, and      
 ultimately find the joy in life.
